OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStarting chilly with an early
OL,6,Fslight frost in places. A dry day
OL,7,Ffollowing with variable amounts of
OL,8,Fhigh cloud but also bright spells, the
OL,9,Fskies becoming generally clearer into
OL,10,Fthe evening. Winds mainly light, with
OL,11,Ftemperatures rising just above average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry with long clear spells
OL,14,Fand turning chilly again, with a touch
OL,15,Fof ground frost in sheltered spots.
OL,16,FWinds mostly light but breezier along
OL,17,Fthe coast and over hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
