OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FDry, fine and warm, the
OL,6,Fsunshine perhaps turning hazier later.
OL,7,FA brisk breeze, especially across
OL,8,Fhills and along the coast, giving a
OL,9,Fnoticeably cooler feel here.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry Wednesday, generally cloudier
OL,13,Falthough still with warm bright or
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Lighter winds. Thursday
OL,15,Fcolder, breezy with sunshine and
OL,16,Fshowers. Friday, cloud, rain and
OL,17,Fstronger winds moving east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
